To run an example of 1D random walk on a filament:
$ ecell3-session 1D.py

To view the simulation results wth the Spatiocyte Visualizer:
$ spatiocyte

To create a movie of the simulation results generated by matplotlib (requires avconv preinstalled):
$ python plot.py

We can use the VLC player to view the movie file:
$ vlc CoordinateLog.csv.mov 
